ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely not recommend PHYS 524 01 to another student, I did not enjoy the class.

In the current form, I would probably recommend it, but with a number of reservations. If the class was reworked with a bit more structure and focus (as described in answers for questions 1 and 2), I think it could be much better.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The course seemed interesting and potentially helpful in the course description, however I don't think the class was helpful at all due to low level of material.
